  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    MRJarExtension
    Extension for defining the behavior and layout of the Multi-release Jar
    Version
    A Version of JVM-language source added to the multi-release JAR.
    VersionDependency
    Configuration of a dependency against a prior major version of Java
    VersionSource
    Configuration of "main" source code or "test" source code targeting a specific version of Java.
    VersionSourceLanguage
    Configuration of a JVM-based language for source targeting a specific version of Java
